  "body": "<p dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Enemies drop ARPG style loot when killed.</strong></span></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1/1000 Chance of a <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Legendary</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2ZaVGRK.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1/200 Chance of an <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">Epic</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pYdcucE.png\" /></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1/200 Chance of an <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Exalted</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K6Xm9EI.png\" /></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1/100 Chance of a <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #00ffff;\">Superb</span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #00ffff;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/a2vnkFD.png\" width=\"287\" height=\"198\" /></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1/50 Chance of a <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">Rare</span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pdPSOpB.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1/25 Chance of an <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #339966;\">Uncommon</span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YtHCFG6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"245\" height=\"156\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1/10 Chance of a<span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #999999;\"> Common</span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #999999;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zo5hBsW.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"249\" height=\"136\" /></span></strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Configuration:</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>All rates are configurable in the arpglootmod.properties file</em></p>\n<p><em>Configuration flags to enable/disable incompatible enchants</em></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><em>Compatibility:</em></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><em>This mod currently uses fixed lists of enchantments.</em></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><em>All mobs tagged as \"monster\" will calculate drops</em></p>",
